outputs.output_descr:
Project goal: The purpose of the Project is mainstreaming human development in Tajikistan through improved policy making and capacities to respond to emerging challenges, and better opportunities to target national development process.

Project outputs: 
Activity Result 1: Improved quality of human development knowledge of students in the institutes of higher education with focus on practical application.
Activity Result 2: Improved capacity to support policy-making, monitoring and research with adequate evidence, especially on local level.

project_title: Mainstreaming Human Development in Tajikistan (Phase II)
